## Models Used

This project may use local LLMs such as `gemma3:12b` with the Ollama runtime.  
**Important**: These models are distributed under their own licenses and usage restrictions. You are 
responsible for reviewing and complying with the license and usage terms of any model you load via Ollama.

- For example, Gemma models are released by Google under the Gemma License Agreement.
- Some models may be for non-commercial use only or research purposes.

This project does not include any pre-downloaded models. It provides tools to run models via Ollama, 
assuming you have the legal right to do so.